The paper discusses the emergence of nodes in evolving networks, which is a topic related to social networks, information retrieval, and data science. Therefore, cs.SI (Social and Information Networks), cs.SD (Software Engineering), and cs.SOC (Social and Information Networks) are likely sub-categories. The paper also uses models and experiments to validate its findings, which falls under cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
